  <description><![CDATA[<p>The stylish resort of Santa Margherita lies just 35km from Genoa. Summer holidays in Santa Margherita offer a stunning location in which to relax and explore the beautiful region of <a data-udi="umb://document/c0a1a2eb5f21493d858ec9013916a8fb" href="/{localLink:umb://document/c0a1a2eb5f21493d858ec9013916a8fb}" title="Liguria">Liguria</a>. A wonderfully peaceful place.</p>
<p>Surrounded by hills, summer holidays in Santa Margherita take you to a resort that evokes the elegance of a bygone era. Magnificent palm lined esplanades lead down to the beach and harbour. The pedestrianised streets are lined with fashionable shops and pavement cafés. And the lovely seafront offers more excellent gelaterie and restaurants. So a summer holiday in Santa Margherita is perfect for pure relaxation.</p>
<p>Summer holidays in Santa Margherita let you immerse yourself in Italian town life, much of which still centres around the picturesque harbour. Here, water sports enthusiasts meet and fishing boats are moored next to luxury yachts. This is where you come to join numerous exciting boat trips. Try <a data-udi="umb://document/0fdd5a3c25b0436daa3b37ce64ccf00b" href="/{localLink:umb://document/0fdd5a3c25b0436daa3b37ce64ccf00b}" title="Rapallo">Rapallo</a> and <a data-udi="umb://document/13b3ee4a5d444c4993a7e2bc1ea88aa2" href="/{localLink:umb://document/13b3ee4a5d444c4993a7e2bc1ea88aa2}" title="Portofino">Portofino</a>, with their intimate seafront piazzas and chic clientele for a start... elegance personified!</p>
<p>Inghams operate a telephone Rep service in Santa Margherita. </p>
<p> </p>]]></description>
