  <listingDescription><![CDATA[<p>The stylish resort of Santa Margherita, 35km from Genoa, offers a stunning location in which to relax and explore the beautiful region of Liguria. Surrounded by hills, the resort evokes the elegance of a bygone era with palm tree-lined esplanades which lead down to the beach and harbour. The pedestrianised streets are lined with fashionable shops and pavement cafés and the seafront offers a further selection of “gelaterie” and restaurants. Much of town life is still centred around the picturesque harbour where water sports enthusiasts meet and fishing boats are moored next to luxury yachts. From here a variety of tempting boat-trips also start. The renowned resorts of Rapallo and Portofino, with their intimate seafront piazzas and chic clientèle are just two of the must-see places to visit.</p>]]></listingDescription>
